{"tid":1402442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Hit and Run","createTime":"2019-08-03T16:19:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T21:07:26.000Z","uid":262263,"like":65,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bf64eec7f8dc71b0b90409169c77c163162a75c3","tid":1402442,"uid":262263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:19:04.000Z","msg":"係啊我係p牌，6月15忍唔住開ac<br />\n睇完先屌，講定先我講野有少少1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係割蓆，唔係屌前線，但我覺得的確需要檢討<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">檢討唔係割蓆唔係屌</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">利申今日孭左幾袋物資去，仲要覺得我係分化撚我真係冇計</span><br />\n<br />\n我覺得今日升旗、紅隧、搭棚，尖沙咀狗屋同保鮮紙防線係<span style=\"font-size: large;\">做得好好</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZE1SjyE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZE1SjyE.png&h=e8d56388&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZaX2GMZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZaX2GMZ.png&h=d35667b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5dSKaFk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5dSKaFk.png&h=69bc99ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C4LPmM0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC4LPmM0.png&h=11e5f6ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nsor for圖唔齊<br />\n<br />\n當然仲有進步空間，令唔好再有手足無謂被補<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">今日Hit and run好正啊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n夜晚做咩又去翻旺角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知前線勇氣係值得尊重，但有鬼都係無可否認(唔好咁天真以為驚畜唔會派畜渾入去啦好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n係前線情緒係好高漲，同樣亦代表有可能會失去冷靜，請大家都要有獨立思考，唔好俾人帶住走<br />\n前線現場判斷，互相討論十分重要，大聲公麻煩收埋佢<br />\n說好的不要大台呢？<br />\n見到手足被捕好心痛啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我認為場運動係時候轉型<br />\nBe water, hit and run, 打游擊(前線組隊，幾時行動做乜野請諗諗老豆搵仔admin們講過乜)<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論<br />\n屌我冇所謂，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好再屌前線，注意討論語氣</span><br />\n<br />\n仲有班所謂屌分化撚既人，麻煩都注意翻語氣，你地語氣差屌人分化只會更分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不割蓆 不分化 不篤灰</span>"},{"pid":"e73b3a77a50c476b91610494e91269b87ee286bf","tid":1402442,"uid":241244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:19:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"420104a75e63b46432bbc6e98a92f9878aac4a66","tid":1402442,"uid":262263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:20:15.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"300057d9b524523e70a3aa8abd7138771f9a1112","tid":1402442,"uid":262263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:21:51.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">理性討論</span>"},{"pid":"78979a84baaca3dc77fa241a8b681ba481e3211a","tid":1402442,"uid":262263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:22:14.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">理性討論</span>"},{"pid":"a27a9997934f454504e64611fc8c23edd5746fb9","tid":1402442,"uid":262263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:22:26.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">理性討論</span>"},{"pid":"ab9baf625aefb4067bd9ff217d81dc21b6f9c905","tid":1402442,"uid":262263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:22:47.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">理性討論</span>"},{"pid":"417f9fd43d6a7938ab263a65d31c27eea6f85d48","tid":1402442,"uid":262263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:23:30.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">理性討論</span>"},{"pid":"720a92a9b6c9de384302d5e4263d51f091a9bb27","tid":1402442,"uid":262263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:25:33.000Z","msg":"推多次<br />\n夜少少再推"},{"pid":"04fe5ff6eb3c7a235402a4cb17eb850057facbe7","tid":1402442,"uid":210140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:26:48.000Z","msg":"今日其實進步左,俾人拉既人少左好多"},{"pid":"2c1980500098bafae23db00b71ef946a95fed329","tid":1402442,"uid":8880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:27:06.000Z","msg":"我覺得今日呢幾個月偷襲先係正路 打遊擊先贏到<br />\n死守 不如搞多裝備打遊擊"},{"pid":"569e395d146ca9eee086e584de1b9e9480658153","tid":1402442,"uid":262263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"04fe5ff6eb3c7a235402a4cb17eb850057facbe7","tid":1402442,"uid":210140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:26:48.000Z","msg":"今日其實進步左,俾人拉既人少左好多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:28:29.000Z","msg":"係，好值得讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我今日覺得入翻旺角有少少送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2138f26c1e6595a4a85f7f1fea71cd824855dada","tid":1402442,"uid":210140,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"569e395d146ca9eee086e584de1b9e9480658153","tid":1402442,"uid":262263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"04fe5ff6eb3c7a235402a4cb17eb850057facbe7","tid":1402442,"uid":210140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:26:48.000Z","msg":"今日其實進步左,俾人拉既人少左好多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:28:29.000Z","msg":"係，好值得讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我今日覺得入翻旺角有少少送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:29:01.000Z","msg":"旺角果下令到有人被捕,但如果唔入旺角真係PERFECT"},{"pid":"f8981517f214898d9d1bd7a3538df6f3ba9886ad","tid":1402442,"uid":8880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"04fe5ff6eb3c7a235402a4cb17eb850057facbe7","tid":1402