131817c68a350","tid":1402442,"uid":260963,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bf64eec7f8dc71b0b90409169c77c163162a75c3","tid":1402442,"uid":262263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:19:04.000Z","msg":"係啊我係p牌，6月15忍唔住開ac<br />\n睇完先屌，講定先我講野有少少1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係割蓆，唔係屌前線，但我覺得的確需要檢討<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">檢討唔係割蓆唔係屌</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">利申今日孭左幾袋物資去，仲要覺得我係分化撚我真係冇計</span><br />\n<br />\n我覺得今日升旗、紅隧、搭棚，尖沙咀狗屋同保鮮紙防線係<span style=\"font-size: large;\">做得好好</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZE1SjyE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZE1SjyE.png&h=e8d56388&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZaX2GMZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZaX2GMZ.png&h=d35667b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5dSKaFk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5dSKaFk.png&h=69bc99ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C4LPmM0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC4LPmM0.png&h=11e5f6ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nsor for圖唔齊<br />\n<br />\n當然仲有進步空間，令唔好再有手足無謂被補<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">今日Hit and run好正啊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n夜晚做咩又去翻旺角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知前線勇氣係值得尊重，但有鬼都係無可否認(唔好咁天真以為驚畜唔會派畜渾入去啦好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n係前線情緒係好高漲，同樣亦代表有可能會失去冷靜，請大家都要有獨立思考，唔好俾人帶住走<br />\n前線現場判斷，互相討論十分重要，大聲公麻煩收埋佢<br />\n說好的不要大台呢？<br />\n見到手足被捕好心痛啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我認為場運動係時候轉型<br />\nBe water, hit and run, 打游擊(前線組隊，幾時行動做乜野請諗諗老豆搵仔admin們講過乜)<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論<br />\n屌我冇所謂，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好再屌前線，注意討論語氣</span><br />\n<br />\n仲有班所謂屌分化撚既人，麻煩都注意翻語氣，你地語氣差屌人分化只會更分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不割蓆 不分化 不篤灰</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:30:40.000Z","msg":"啱啊 冷靜啲 唔好見到意見就話人鶭<br />\n分化 可能brainstorm吓有更好戰略"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:34:55.000Z","msg":"啱啱我話前線有人話散俾人屌，條友係咁話前線尊重要走既，我做咩唔尊重前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁唔講屌唔係尊重先，又話齊上齊落又唔肯討論做咩喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3afad0cba435ecd6154dbc3c975ca817eb99fca","tid":1402442,"uid":262263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8da2bf00d052a6861ff6b727f673d3ab373a2d9","tid":1402442,"uid":2429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KfDUx7L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKfDUx7L.jpg&h=1e593f7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:36:03.000Z","msg":"謝提圖，己save<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec00675affabdb517f220f31615c13969e2b037d","tid":1402442,"uid":262263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1f3a16bc086c39674189153811797bb357891bd","tid":1402442,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04e1827cc230b5f0315c339e2a04a1439bed3acf","tid":1402442,"uid":262263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd74d0fbcd0d5ffd04de6331e9d1f7479c1468fb","tid":1402442,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:31:00.000Z","msg":"其實ROAD BLOCK既終極目的唔係守,而係令到班狗前進唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:33:07.000Z","msg":"set完就走，hit and run<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:33:48.000Z"